text: Market News March 6, 2018 / 2:09 PM / Updated 12 minutes ago BRIEF-TMX Group Reports All TMX Equities Marketplaces Volume Was 12.6 Bln For Feb 2018 Vs 13.47 Bln In Feb 2017 Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 6 (Reuters) - Tmx Group Ltd: * TMX GROUP LTD - ALL TMX EQUITIES MARKETPLACES VOLUME WAS 12.6 BILLION FOR FEB 2018 VERSUS 13.47 BILLION IN FEB 2017 * TMX GROUP LTD - ALL TMX EQUITIES MARKETPLACES TRANSACTIONS WAS 24.1 MILLION FOR FEB 2018 VERSUS 20.1 MILLION IN FEB 2017 * TMX GROUP LTD - ALL TMX EQUITIES MARKETPLACES DAILY AVERAGE VOLUME WAS 663.0 MILLION FOR FEB 2018 VERSUS 709.0 MILLION IN FEB 2017 Source text for Eikon:
